      "content": "i'm tired of doctors telling me everything is gonna be fine when it clearly isn't. i just want the truth for once. i have this chronic depression that just won't lift no matter what meds or therapy i try. can you just be real with me... is there actually any hope for someone like me to actually recover, or is science just pretending?",
